    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i've been looking at humanitarian reach for a while and i'm thinking about making a significant new contribution next quarter. but honestly, i've seen so many stories lately about NGOs wasting funds on massive office buildings and marketing instead of actually helping people. how efficient are you guys really when it comes to getting money to the ground?",
