      "content": "85% is a strong number, but I've heard some conflicting reports from auditors recently about the actual split in your latest quarterly report. They were suggesting that a much larger chunk was diverted to administrative and marketing expenses. Can you look into the specific breakdown for the most recent $1M influx and confirm exactly what percentage was allocated to direct field aid versus overhead?",
